(2041, 327, 3, 'Add the melted, cooled chocolate and beat it in. Gradually add the sifted flour to the batter.Beat the egg whites until stiff but not dry and fold them into the mixture.'),
(2042, 331, 2, 'Pour black beans into a saucepan with salt, pepper and garlic powder to taste'),
(2043, 329, 3, 'Mix in the flour until just combined.'),
(2044, 327, 4, 'Pour batter into one ungreased 9 inch springform pan.'),
(2045, 328, 2, 'Place in a mixing bowl and set aside.'),
