(2051, 331, 4, 'Spread the pizza dough to desired thickness on the bottom and sides of skillet'),
(2052, 327, 6, 'Add the coffee and beat well.  Sift and add the confectioners sugar and 1 teaspoon vanilla.'),
(2053, 330, 2, 'Drain and set aside.Line a 9-by-5-inch loaf baking pan with parchment paper and set aside.In your food processor add the base ingredients and pulse until combined, about 30 seconds.'),
(2054, 328, 3, 'Mix together BBQ seasoning and add to jackfruit. Toss to coat.'),
(2055, 332, 1, 'Place egg in a saucepan and cover with cold water. Bring water to a boil and immediately remove from heat. Cover and let eggs stand in hot water for 10 to 12 minutes.'),
