(2060, 327, 7, 'Spread the warm icing on the top and sides of the torte'),
(2061, 331, 5, 'Spread a layer of refried beans on the pizza crust'),
(2062, 329, 6, 'Remove one of the wrapped sections of dough from the refrigerator.'),
(2063, 332, 3, 'Place the chopped eggs in a bowl, and stir in the mayonnaise, mustard and green onion. Season with salt, pepper and paprika. Stir and serve on your favorite bread or crackers.'),
(2064, 328, 5, 'Add BBQ sauce and thin with enough water to make a sauce. Stir and reduce heat to low- medium and cook for about 20 minutes (up to 35 minutes on low for a deeper flavor).'),
(2065, 330, 4, 'Place the cheesecake layer in your food processor and pulse until smooth, about 2-3 minutes depending on your food processor. Evenly spread this mixture over the base layer.In a small bowl mix the topping ingredients. Distribute the topping over the cheesecake layer and with your hands press down li'),
