(2068, 331, 6, 'Sprinkle on a layer of shredded cheese and taco meat'),
(2069, 329, 7, 'Roll out to a roughly 10\" square. The dough is sticky, so be sure to flour your surface and your rolling pin really well.'),
(2070, 328, 6, 'Remove lid and stir occasionally. TIP: For finer texture, use two forks to shred the jackfruit as it cooks down.In the meantime, make slaw by adding all ingredients except vegetables (avocado through salt + pepper) to a small mixing bowl and whisk to combine. Thin with water until a thick sauce is m'),
(2071, 330, 5, 'Place the cheesecake in the freezer for at least 3-4 hours.Thaw cheesecake for 15-20 minutes before serving. At this time you can cut cheesecake into 2-3 inch. Store leftover cheesecake covered in the freezer.'),
