(2125, 340, 7, 'Pour 1/2 cup of the salsa verde onto the bottom of a 9x13 inch baking dish.Wrap the tortillas in a damp paper towel and microwave for one minute. Spoon a little of the chicken mixture down the center of each tortilla, tuck and roll, placing the tortilla, seam side down, into the baking dish.'),
