(2129, 340, 11, 'In a medium bowl, gently toss together all the ingredients. Keep stored in the fridge for up 2 days.'),
(2130, 346, 1, 'Preheat oven to 350 degrees F.In large pot of boiling salted water, cook the macaroni to al dente (approximately 7 minutes). Strain and place on a lightly oiled sheet pan.While the macaroni is cooking, in a separate pot, melt 3 tablespoons of butter and whisk in the flour. Continue to cook over low '),
