(3835, 636, 2, 'Add pasta and cheese, adding additional wine or chicken broth if liquid is gone.Cook for 20 -45 minutes until noodles are cooked.Do not overcook!As soon as the casserole is done, remove your crock from heating element so the pasta won’t continue to cook.Sprinkle with additional cheese if desired.'),
(3836, 637, 1, 'Preheat oven to 375F.Bring the water to boil in a large pot or dutch oven. While it comes to a boil, prep the beans. Fill a large bowl with ice water.'),
