(3860, 638, 2, 'Let cool slightly then toss with garlic, pesto and dressing.Cook zucchini in covered microwavable container on high 2 minutes or until just tender and bright green.Toss blanched zucchini, tomatoes, onion and peas into pasta and stir to combine. Gently fold in drained salmon; season to taste with sal'),
