(3969, 660, 5, 'Spread on a parchment-lined baking sheet and roast for 20 minutes, or until tender and starting to brown. Meanwhile, in a small bowl, whisk together the red pepper flakes, parsley, basil, capers, and remaining 1/4 cup olive oil. Season to taste with salt.In a large bowl, toss together the beans, whe'),
